<br>
I've played several Midgard combos and from my experience, the skald/healer is the best, and even more so if the shammy is out of the question.  <br>
<br>
Downtime is minimal using the Provoke style and the healer's purity.  The trick to leveling fast is to find high orange/low red mobs and mow through them one at a time.  You will almost never die unless three or more aggro, and even then you will have a chance with your healers insta-heals and insta-mezzing, not to mention your skalds two insta-shouts and one insta-mez (great for quickly pulling aggro off your healer).<br>
<br>
Be sure to get your healer's mend skills up first to get the insta-heals, then work on the pac for the insta-mezzes.  Best MAP (mend/aug/pac) imo is 35/15/38.<br>
